---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Location — On the Brooklyn Waterfront | Tennis Terminal"
  description="Tennis Terminal is opening on Furman St, right on the Brooklyn waterfront — steps from the ferry and greenway. Exact address announced to our waitlist first."
  path="/location"
>
  <section style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,84px) 24px clamp(24px,4vw,40px)">
    <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);margin-bottom:16px">The space</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(38px,5.4vw,60px);line-height:1.04;max-width:18ch">Four bays on the Brooklyn waterfront</h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:clamp(17px,2.2vw,20px);line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:20px;max-width:54ch;text-wrap:pretty">A bright, warm room right on the water — big windows, a real cushioned court surface, and enough net height to actually swing. Each bay is yours alone for your booked hour.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- GALLERY -->
  <section style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px clamp(40px,6vw,64px)">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:16px">
      <div style="grid-column:span 2;min-width:0;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);min-height:300px"><img src="/assets/photos/empty-bay.png" alt="Empty indoor bay at Tennis Terminal with windows onto the Brooklyn waterfront" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block" /></div>
      <div style="border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);min-height:300px"><img src="/assets/photos/pickleball.png" alt="Two friends sharing a high-five over the net after pickleball at Tennis Terminal" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block" /></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AMENITIES -->
  <section style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px clamp(40px,6vw,64px)">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:22px"><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:18px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">Private bays</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-ink-500);margin-top:6px">Just your group, every time</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:22px"><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:18px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">Gear on hand</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-ink-500);margin-top:6px">Loaner racquets, paddles &amp; balls</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:22px"><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:18px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">Both sports</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-ink-500);margin-top:6px">Bays convert in seconds</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--tt-white);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:12px;padding:22px"><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:18px;color:var(--tt-court-ink)">Open late</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--tt-ink-500);margin-top:6px">7am to 11pm, daily</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOCATION + GETTING THERE -->
  <section style="background:var(--tt-white);border-top:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade)">
    <div style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,84px) 24px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:clamp(32px,5vw,56px);align-items:center">
      <div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);margin-bottom:14px">Getting here</div>
        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.8vw,40px);line-height:1.08">On Furman St, Brooklyn waterfront</h2>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:17px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:16px">We're opening on Furman St, right on the Brooklyn waterfront path — a short walk from the ferry and a straight shot down the greenway by bike. The exact address goes out to our waitlist first.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;margin-top:24px">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:baseline"><span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);min-width:74px">Ferry</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">NYC Ferry along the Brooklyn waterfront — steps away</span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:baseline"><span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);min-width:74px">Subway</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">2/3/4/5/R to Borough Hall or Court St — 12 min</span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:baseline"><span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);min-width:74px">Bike</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">Citi Bike docks nearby · racks on site</span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:baseline"><span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);min-width:74px">Hours</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-ink-700)">Every day, 7am–11pm</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);min-height:340px;height:340px;position:relative">
        <iframe src="/map.html" title="Map: general area on the Brooklyn waterfront" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;border:0;display:block"></iframe>
        <span style="position:absolute;bottom:16px;left:16px;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-ink-500);background:rgba(253,246,230,0.9);padding:6px 10px;border-radius:6px;pointer-events:none">Full address announced soon</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background:var(--tt-play-green)">
    <div style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,80px) 24px;text-align:center">
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);line-height:1.1;color:var(--tt-honey-cream)">Come see it in person</h2>
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.9;margin-top:14px">Join the waitlist and you'll be first through the door — free hour included.</p>
      <a href="/join" style="display:inline-block;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-court-ink);background:var(--tt-honey-cream);padding:15px 30px;border-radius:10px;margin-top:26px">Join the waitlist →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
